highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Top Songs Malaysia. “Golden” is the highest at #3.
“GO!” by CORTIS is the highest new entry on Top Songs Malaysia at #35.
“Heather” by Conan Gray has been on Top Songs Malaysia the longest, at 272 weeks straight.
“Takkan Pergi” by Hyper Act is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Malaysia, up 69 spots at #82.
